public abstract class PropertyValue<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable, IPropertyValue<T>

Abstract class for a property value. Every PropertyValue must derive from this one.

owner

protected ElementInstance owner
Pointer to the element that owns this property (optional). If it is set to null, the property does not belong to any element. In this case no assignement controls are executed.

propertyName

The property name of this value in the owner element (optional, but mandatory if owner is assigned).
